    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who create artistic drawings and plans for the construction or creation of something according to aesthetic or functional criteria; those who create plans or concepts for subsequent implementation of graphic works, objects, structures, systems, or conceptual schemes.</Note_Text>
